parameters: \TA[1]...It's a bit late to ask, but why are you here?

\TA[1]Didn't I say that you can stick with me as much as you
want, except during battles?
\TA[1]Even so, nothing surprising is happening at all.

\TA[1]According to the police data, it is indeed a place where
missing persons frequently occur.

\TA[1]Putting aside how you know that... I wish it was just a
rumor.
\TA[1]If it's just a rumor, then there shouldn't be any victims.

\TA[1]They don't disappear that easily. If there were missing
persons every day, it would have already become big news.

\TA[1]Since I heard the story, I will patrol every night for at
least a week.
\TA[1]How about it? Are you getting tired of all the boring work?

\TA[1]Where?! Where did they disappear?! (Damn it, if only I had
been more careful...!)

\TA[1](Let's reflect on that later... There's a faint moisture
over there.)
\TA[1]Sewer? Why is it in a place like this...!
\TA[1]Wait, I'm going to help you right now!
